sequenceDiagram
    participant N as Nagios
    participant M as MySQL
    participant W as NGINX
    N->>M: Check Connection (TCP:3306)
    M-->>N: Connection OK
    N->>M: Check Database
    M-->>N: Database Status
    N->>W: Check HTTP (Port:8081)
    W-->>N: HTTP Response
    N->>W: Check Process
    W-->>N: Process Status
    Note over N: Update Status
    Note over N: Generate Alerts if needed